<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title }} - Symfony 8.0</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .demo-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .demo-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .demo-header h1 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .demo-header p {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .version-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .feature-list li {
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border: 1px solid #b3d9ff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .code-block {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: monospace;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="demo-container">
        <div class="demo-header">
            <h1>üîç Twig Inspector Bundle <span class="version-badge">Symfony 8.0</span></h1>
            <p>Symfony Bundle Demo</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome!</h2>
            <p>{{ message }}</p>

            <h3 class="mt-4">How to Use:</h3>
            <ul class="feature-list">
                {% for item in items %}
                    <li>{{ item }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>üìù Instructions:</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Look at the bottom of the page for the Symfony Web Profiler toolbar</li>
                    <li>Find the <code>&lt;/&gt;</code> icon (Twig Inspector)</li>
                    <li>Check the "enable" checkbox to activate Twig Inspector</li>
                    <li>The page will reload with inspection enabled</li>
                    <li>Hover over any HTML element to see which template rendered it</li>
                    <li>Click on elements to open the template in your IDE</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4">
                <h3>Example Template Structure</h3>
                <p>This page uses the following template structure:</p>
                <div class="code-block">
                    templates/demo/home.html.twig<br>
                    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Extends base template<br>
                    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Contains blocks and includes
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4">
                <h3>Template Blocks</h3>
                <p>This template demonstrates various Twig features:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Variables:</strong> {{ title }}, {{ message }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Loops:</strong> Iterating over items array</li>
                    <li><strong>Includes:</strong> Can include other templates</li>
                    <li><strong>Blocks:</strong> Extendable template structure</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 text-center">
            <small class="text-muted">
                Powered by <a href="https://github.com/nowo-tech/twig-inspector-bundle" target="_blank">Twig Inspector Bundle</a>
            </small>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
